item.title: Trendz
item.description: Trendz (part 1 & 2) Preamble This challenge is divided into four parts, three webs and a reverse. I’m excited to share that I managed to solve the first two webs! I’ll insert them all in a write-up, trying to explain them in the way the author thought. I admit I did not solve them in order, but I’m eager to see how they fit together. The application was written in Go using templates and a JWT authentication, and it’s write well!
